Darshan B: Just visit the site https://hpe.sharepoint.com/sites/F3/COO/procurementcentral/ariba/sitePages/home.aspx
once.

1)	Click on the Orange color tab at the bottom right stating Connect to GP Help
2)	Click on the Get Help play button > under GP Help
3)	Click on Procurement Tools-> Ariba-> Requisition or Order and it will take you to the new tab or page
Here you should find the option to directly connect to the ariba support team at the bottom or submit a case to the team with your request.



